headline: Discover Delays Filing Over Accounting Disagreement With SEC
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Discover Financial Services said it will miss a deadline to file its quarterly report with regulators, citing disagreements with the Securities and Exchange Commission over its accounting treatment of a credit-card misclassification blunder.
